@startuml detect_communities

' Component definitions
participant "Business User" as User
participant "DetectCommunitiesUI\n(boundary/projects_ui.py\ndetect_communities())" as DetectCommunitiesUI

' Sequence flow
User -> DetectCommunitiesUI: Select detect communities\nfrom project SNA menu
activate DetectCommunitiesUI

DetectCommunitiesUI -> DetectCommunitiesUI: Render detect_communities.html
activate DetectCommunitiesUI
note right: Template includes:\n- Algorithm selection options\n- Network visualization placeholder\n- Modularity score display\n- Community count display
deactivate DetectCommunitiesUI

DetectCommunitiesUI --> User: Display detect communities page\nwith algorithm options
deactivate DetectCommunitiesUI

User -> DetectCommunitiesUI: View network visualization
activate DetectCommunitiesUI

DetectCommunitiesUI --> User: Display interactive network\nwith nodes and edges\n(community clusters if detection ran)
deactivate DetectCommunitiesUI

User -> DetectCommunitiesUI: View modularity score\nand community count
activate DetectCommunitiesUI

DetectCommunitiesUI --> User: Display metrics\n(modularity score, community count)
deactivate DetectCommunitiesUI

@enduml
